# Backend API URL.
# - Web: Leave unset. The app uses the same host as the page on port 3000.
# - Expo Go on a physical device: REQUIRED. Set to your computer's LAN IPv4 so the phone can reach the backend.
#   Example: EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.100:3000
#   Windows: ipconfig  |  macOS/Linux: ifconfig or ip addr
# - Simulator/emulator: optional; defaults to http://127.0.0.1:3000
#
# Do NOT use the literal text YOUR_IPv4 or YOUR_IP as the hostname â€“ replace with your actual IP.
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://YOUR_IPv4:3000
